INSERT INTO `pokemon_info` VALUES (1,'green',0,50,45,'이상해씨','Bulbasaur','씨앗포켓몬','Seed Pokémon','양지에서 낮잠 자는 모습을 볼 수 있다.\n태양의 빛을 많이 받으면\n등의 씨앗이 크게 자란다.','Bulbasaur can be seen napping in bright sunlight.\nThere is a seed on its back. By soaking up the sun’s rays,\nthe seed grows progressively larger.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/1.png'),(2,'green',0,50,45,'이상해풀','Ivysaur','씨앗포켓몬','Seed Pokémon','꽃봉오리를 지탱하기 위해 하반신이 강해진다.\n양지에서 가만히 있는 시간이 길어지면\n드디어 커다란 꽃이 필 때다.','There is a bud on this Pokémon’s back. To support its weight,\nIvysaur’s legs and trunk grow thick and strong.\nIf it starts spending more time lying in the sunlight,\nit’s a sign that the bud will bloom into a large flower soon.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/2.png'),(3,'green',0,50,45,'이상해꽃','Venusaur','씨앗포켓몬','Seed Pokémon','충분한 영양분과 태양의 빛이\n꽃의 색을 선명하게 만든다고 한다.\n꽃의 향기는 사람의 마음을 치유한다.','There is a large flower on Venusaur’s back. The flower is said\nto take on vivid colors if it gets plenty of nutrition and sunlight.\nThe flower’s aroma soothes the emotions of people.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/3.png'),(4,'red',0,50,45,'파이리','Charmander','도롱뇽포켓몬','Lizard Pokémon','꼬리의 불꽃은 기분을 표현한다.\n즐거울 때는 흔들흔들 불꽃이 흔들리고\n화가 났을 때는 활활 맹렬히 불타오른다.','The flame that burns at the tip of its tail is an indication\nof its emotions. The flame wavers when Charmander\nis enjoying itself. If the Pokémon becomes enraged,\nthe flame burns fiercely.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/4.png'),(5,'red',0,50,45,'리자드','Charmeleon','화염포켓몬','Flame Pokémon','날카로운 발톱으로 봐주지 않고 때려눕힌다.\n강한 적을 만나면 기분이 고양되며\n꼬리의 불꽃이 푸르스름하게 불타오른다.','Charmeleon mercilessly destroys its foes using its sharp claws.\nIf it encounters a strong foe, it turns aggressive.\nIn this excited state, the flame at the tip of its tail flares with a\nbluish white color.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/5.png'),(6,'red',0,50,45,'리자몽','Charizard','화염포켓몬','Flame Pokémon','강한 상대를 찾아 하늘을 날아다닌다.\n무엇이든 다 녹여버리는 고열의 불꽃을\n자신보다 약한 자에게 들이대지 않는다.','Charizard flies around the sky in search of powerful opponents.\nIt breathes fire of such great heat that it melts anything.\nHowever, it never turns its fiery breath on any opponent\nweaker than itself.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/6.png'),(7,'blue',0,50,45,'꼬부기','Squirtle','꼬마거북포켓몬','Tiny Turtle Pokémon','등껍질의 역할은 몸을 지키는 것뿐만이 아니다.\n둥그런 모양과 표면의 홈이 물의\n저항을 줄여서 빠르게 헤엄칠 수 있다.','Squirtle’s shell is not merely used for protection.\nThe shell’s rounded shape and the grooves on its surface\nhelp minimize resistance in water, enabling this Pokémon\nto swim at high speeds.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/7.png'),(8,'blue',0,50,45,'어니부기','Wartortle','거북포켓몬','Turtle Pokémon','푹신한 털로 덮인 큰 꼬리는\n오래 살수록 깊은 색으로 변한다.\n등껍질의 상처는 강자임을 증명한다.','Its tail is large and covered with a rich, thick fur. The tail\nbecomes increasingly deeper in color as Wartortle ages.\nThe scratches on its shell are evidence of this Pokémon’s\ntoughness as a battler.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/8.png'),(9,'blue',0,50,45,'거북왕','Blastoise','껍질포켓몬','Shellfish Pokémon','등껍질의 분사구로 하는 조준은 정확하다.\n물 탄환으로 50m 떨어진\n빈 캔을 명중시킬 수 있다.','Blastoise has water spouts that protrude from its shell.\nThe water spouts are very accurate. They can shoot bullets of\nwater with enough accuracy to strike empty cans from a\ndistance of over 160 feet.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/9.png'),(10,'green',0,50,255,'캐터피','Caterpie','애벌레포켓몬','Worm Pokémon','몸보다 커다란 잎사귀를 순식간에\n먹어치울 정도의 식욕을 지녔다.\n더듬이로 강렬한 냄새를 피운다.','Caterpie has a voracious appetite. It can devour leaves bigger\nthan its body right before your eyes. From its antenna, this\nPokémon releases a terrifically strong odor.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10.png'),(11,'green',0,50,120,'단데기','Metapod','번데기포켓몬','Cocoon Pokémon','몸의 껍질은 철판처럼 단단하다.\n움직임이 적은 것은 껍질 안에서 부드러운\n몸이 진화 준비를 하고 있어서다.','The shell covering this Pokémon’s body is as hard as an\niron slab. Metapod does not move very much. It stays still\nbecause it is preparing its soft innards for evolution inside\nthe hard shell.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/11.png'),(12,'white',0,50,45,'버터플','Butterfree','나비포켓몬','Butterfly Pokémon','맛있는 꽃의 꿀을 찾는 능력이\n뛰어나서 사는 곳에서 10km 떨어진 장소에\n핀 꽃에서 꿀을 모아 옮긴다.','Butterfree has a superior ability to search for delicious honey\nfrom flowers. It can even search out, extract, and carry honey\nfrom flowers that are blooming over six miles from its nest.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/12.png'),(13,'brown',0,70,255,'뿔충이','Weedle','송충이포켓몬','Hairy Bug Pokémon','굉장히 예민한 후각을 지니고 있다.\n좋아하는 잎사귀인지 싫어하는 잎사귀인지\n크고 빨간 코로 냄새 맡아 구별한다.','Weedle has an extremely acute sense of smell. It is capable of\ndistinguishing its favorite kinds of leaves from those it dislikes\njust by sniffing with its big red proboscis (nose).','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/13.png'),(14,'yellow',0,70,120,'딱충이','Kakuna','번데기포켓몬','Cocoon Pokémon','거의 움직이지 않고 나무에 매달려 있지만\n내부는 진화 준비로 굉장히 바쁜 상태다.\n그 증거로 몸이 뜨거워져 있다.','Kakuna remains virtually immobile as it clings to a tree.\nHowever, on the inside, it is extremely busy as it prepares for\nits coming evolution. This is evident from how hot the shell\nbecomes to the touch.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/14.png'),(15,'yellow',0,70,45,'독침붕','Beedrill','독벌포켓몬','Poison Bee Pokémon','영역에 대한 집착이 매우 강해서 독침붕이\n사는 곳에는 가까이 가지 않는 것이 신상에 좋다.\n화나면 집단으로 습격해 온다.','Beedrill is extremely territorial. No one should ever approach\nits nest—this is for their own safety. If angered, they will attack\nin a furious swarm.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/15.png'),(16,'brown',0,70,255,'구구','Pidgey','아기새포켓몬','Tiny Bird Pokémon','방향 감각이 매우 뛰어나서\n아무리 멀리 떨어진 곳에서도 헤매지 않고\n자신의 둥지까지 찾아 돌아올 수 있다.','Pidgey has an extremely sharp sense of direction. It is capable\nof unerringly returning home to its nest, however far it may be\nremoved from its familiar surroundings.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/16.png'),(17,'brown',0,70,120,'피죤','Pidgeotto','새포켓몬','Bird Pokémon','넓은 영역을 날며 순찰한다.\n영역을 침범하는 상대는 용서하지 않는다.\n날카로운 발톱으로 철저히 혼내준다.','Pidgeotto claims a large area as its own territory.\nThis Pokémon flies around, patrolling its living space.\nIf its territory is violated, it shows no mercy in thoroughly\npunishing the foe with its sharp claws.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/17.png'),(18,'brown',0,70,45,'피죤투','Pidgeot','새포켓몬','Bird Pokémon','아름답게 윤이 나는 깃털을 가진 포켓몬이다.\n머리 깃털의 아름다움에 마음을 빼앗겨\n피죤투를 기르는 트레이너도 많다.','This Pokémon has a dazzling plumage of beautifully\nglossy feathers. Many Trainers are captivated by the\nstriking beauty of the feathers on its head, compelling\nthem to choose Pidgeot as their Pokémon.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/18.png'),(19,'purple',0,70,255,'꼬렛','Rattata','쥐포켓몬','Mouse Pokémon','경계심이 매우 강해서 자고 있을 때도\n귀를 움직여 주변의 소리를 듣고 있다.\n어디에든 자리를 잡고 둥지를 만든다.','Rattata is cautious in the extreme. Even while it is asleep,\nit constantly listens by moving its ears around. It is not picky\nabout where it lives—it will make its nest anywhere.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/19.png'),(20,'brown',0,70,127,'레트라','Raticate','쥐포켓몬','Mouse Pokémon','튼튼한 이빨은 계속 자라기 때문에\n바위나 큰 나무를 갉아서 갈아낸다.\n집의 벽을 갉아 놓기도 한다.','Raticate’s sturdy fangs grow steadily. To keep them ground\ndown, it gnaws on rocks and logs. It may even chew on the\nwalls of houses.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/20.png'),(21,'brown',0,70,255,'깨비참','Spearow','아기새포켓몬','Tiny Bird Pokémon','큰 울음소리는 1km 밖까지 도달한다.\n여기저기에서 높은 울음소리가 들릴 때는\n동료에게 위험을 알리고 있는 신호다.','Spearow has a very loud cry that can be heard over\nhalf a mile away. If its high, keening cry is heard echoing all\naround, it is a sign that they are warning each other of danger.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/21.png'),(22,'brown',0,70,90,'깨비드릴조','Fearow','부리포켓몬','Beak Pokémon','긴 목과 부리는 땅이나 물 안에\n있는 먹이를 잡기 편리하다.\n가늘고 긴 부리로 능숙히 집는다.','Fearow is recognized by its long neck and elongated beak.\nThey are conveniently shaped for catching prey in soil\nor water. It deftly moves its long and skinny beak to\npluck prey.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/22.png'),(23,'purple',0,70,255,'아보','Ekans','뱀포켓몬','Snake Pokémon','빙빙 몸을 말고 쉬고 있는 것은\n어떤 방향에서 적이 습격해 와도\n빠르게 머리를 틀어 위협할 수 있기 때문이다.','Ekans curls itself up in a spiral while it rests. Assuming this\nposition allows it to quickly respond to a threat from any\ndirection with a glare from its upraised head.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/23.png'),(24,'purple',0,70,90,'아보크','Arbok','코브라포켓몬','Cobra Pokémon','조이는 힘이 매우 강력하다.\n드럼통도 납작하게 짜부라트린다.\n휘감기면 도망가는 것이 불가능하다.','This Pokémon is terrifically strong in order to constrict things\nwith its body. It can even flatten steel oil drums.\nOnce Arbok wraps its body around its foe, escaping its\ncrunching embrace is impossible.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/24.png'),(25,'yellow',0,50,190,'피카츄','Pikachu','쥐포켓몬','Mouse Pokémon','처음 보는 것에게는 전격을 맞춘다.\n새까맣게 탄 나무열매가 떨어져 있다는 것은\n전격의 세기를 조절하지 못했다는 증거다.','Whenever Pikachu comes across something new,\nit blasts it with a jolt of electricity. If you come across a\nblackened berry, it’s evidence that this Pokémon mistook the\nintensity of its charge.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/25.png'),(26,'yellow',0,50,75,'라이츄','Raichu','쥐포켓몬','Mouse Pokémon','전기 주머니에 전기가 넘칠 정도로 차면\n꼬리를 땅에 닿게 하여 방전한다.\n사는 곳 근처의 땅에는 탄 흔적이 있다.','If the electrical sacs become excessively charged,\nRaichu plants its tail in the ground and discharges.\nScorched patches of ground will be found near this\nPokémon’s nest.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/26.png'),(27,'yellow',0,50,255,'모래두지','Sandshrew','쥐포켓몬','Mouse Pokémon','몸이 수분을 효율적으로 흡수하기 때문에\n건조한 모래땅에서도 문제없다.\n몸을 둥글게 만들어 적의 공격을 막는다.','Sandshrew’s body is configured to absorb water without waste,\nenabling it to survive in an arid desert. This Pokémon curls up\nto protect itself from its enemies.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/27.png'),(28,'yellow',0,50,90,'고지','Sandslash','쥐포켓몬','Mouse Pokémon','몸의 가시는 피부가 딱딱해진 것이다.\n1년에 1회 오래된 가시가 빠지고\n새로운 가시가 밑에서 돋아난다.','Sandslash’s body is covered by tough spikes, which are\nhardened sections of its hide. Once a year, the old spikes\nfall out, to be replaced with new spikes that grow out from\nbeneath the old ones.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/28.png'),(29,'blue',0,50,235,'니드런♀','Nidoran♀','독침포켓몬','Poison Pin Pokémon','작은 몸을 지키기 위해 강력한\n독침이 발달한 것이라 여겨진다.\n화가 나면 뿔 끝에서 맹독을 뿜는다.','Nidoran♀ has barbs that secrete a powerful poison.\nThey are thought to have developed as protection for\nthis small-bodied Pokémon. When enraged, it releases\na horrible toxin from its horn.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/29.png'),(30,'blue',0,50,120,'니드리나','Nidorina','독침포켓몬','Poison Pin Pokémon','동료나 가족과 함께일 때는 서로\n상처 입히지 않도록 가시를 세우지 않는다.\n동료와 떨어지면 불안해하는 것 같다.','When Nidorina are with their friends or family, they keep their\nbarbs tucked away to prevent hurting each other.\nThis Pokémon appears to become nervous if separated from\nthe others.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/30.png'),(31,'blue',0,50,45,'니드퀸','Nidoqueen','드릴포켓몬','Drill Pokémon','단단한 비늘로 뒤덮인 몸을 부딪쳐서\n상대를 튕겨내는 공격이 특기다.\n자식을 지킬 때 가장 강하다.','Nidoqueen’s body is encased in extremely hard scales.\nIt is adept at sending foes flying with harsh tackles.\nThis Pokémon is at its strongest when it is defending its young.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/31.png'),(32,'purple',0,50,235,'니드런♂','Nidoran♂','독침포켓몬','Poison Pin Pokémon','귀를 움직이는 근육이 발달되어 있어서\n어떤 방향으로든 자유로이 귀를 움직일 수 있다.\n희미한 소리도 빠트리지 않고 듣는 포켓몬이다.','Nidoran♂ has developed muscles for moving its ears. Thanks\nto them, the ears can be freely moved in any direction. Even\nthe slightest sound does not escape this Pokémon’s notice.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/32.png'),(33,'purple',0,50,120,'니드리노','Nidorino','독침포켓몬','Poison Pin Pokémon','다이아몬드보다 단단한 뿔을 지녔다.\n적의 기척을 느끼면 등에 달린 가시를\n일제히 세우고 전력을 다해 맞선다.','Nidorino has a horn that is harder than a diamond. If it senses\na hostile presence, all the barbs on its back bristle up at once,\nand it challenges the foe with all its might.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/33.png'),(34,'purple',0,50,45,'니드킹','Nidoking','드릴포켓몬','Drill Pokémon','두꺼운 꼬리는 한 번 휘두르면 튼튼한\n철탑도 꺾어 버리는 엄청난 파괴력을 지녔다.\n한 번 날뛰기 시작하면 손쓸 수 없다.','Nidoking’s thick tail packs enormously destructive power.\nWith one swing, it can topple a metal transmission tower.\nOnce this Pokémon goes on a rampage, there is no stopping it.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/34.png'),(35,'pink',0,140,150,'삐삐','Clefairy','요정포켓몬','Fairy Pokémon','보름달 밤에는 기운차게 논다.\n동틀 녘에 지친 삐삐들은 조용한\n산속에서 동료와 바짝 붙어 잠잔다.','On every night of a full moon, groups of this Pokémon come\nout to play. When dawn arrives, the tired Clefairy return to their\nquiet mountain retreats and go to sleep nestled up against\neach other.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/35.png'),(36,'pink',0,140,25,'픽시','Clefable','요정포켓몬','Fairy Pokémon','날개를 사용하여 날아가듯 뛰어간다.\n물 위를 걷는 것도 할 수 있다.\n조용한 달밤에 호수를 걷는다.','Clefable moves by skipping lightly as if it were flying using its\nwings. Its bouncy step lets it even walk on water. It is known\nto take strolls on lakes on quiet, moonlit nights.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/36.png'),(37,'brown',0,50,190,'식스테일','Vulpix','여우포켓몬','Fox Pokémon','태어났을 때는 하얀 꼬리가 한 개다.\n애정을 많이 받으면 꼬리가\n6개로 나뉘며 멋지게 말린다.','At the time of its birth, Vulpix has one white tail. The tail\nseparates into six if this Pokémon receives plenty of love\nfrom its Trainer. The six tails become magnificently curled.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/37.png'),(38,'yellow',0,50,75,'나인테일','Ninetales','여우포켓몬','Fox Pokémon','새빨간 눈은 괴상한 빛을 발산하여\n상대의 마음을 자유로이 조종한다.\n1000년을 산다고 전해진다.','Ninetales casts a sinister light from its bright red eyes to gain\ntotal control over its foe’s mind. This Pokémon is said to live\nfor a thousand years.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/38.png'),(39,'pink',0,50,170,'푸린','Jigglypuff','풍선포켓몬','Balloon Pokémon','목소리의 파장을 자유로이 바꿀 수 있는\n성대가 있어서 상대가 가장 졸리게 되는\n파장으로 노래를 부를 수 있다.','Jigglypuff’s vocal cords can freely adjust the wavelength of its\nvoice. This Pokémon uses this ability to sing at precisely the\nright wavelength to make its foes most drowsy.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/39.png'),(40,'pink',0,50,50,'푸크린','Wigglytuff','풍선포켓몬','Balloon Pokémon','크고 동그란 눈동자 표면에는\n항상 얇은 눈물 막이 쳐져 있다.\n먼지가 들어가도 바로 씻겨 나간다.','Wigglytuff has large, saucerlike eyes. The surfaces of its eyes\nare always covered with a thin layer of tears. If any dust gets in\nthis Pokémon’s eyes, it is quickly washed away.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/40.png'),(41,'purple',0,50,255,'주뱃','Zubat','박쥐포켓몬','Bat Pokémon','낮에 어두운 곳에서 가만히 있는 것은\n긴 시간 동안 햇빛을 받으면\n전신에 가벼운 화상을 입기 때문이다.','Zubat remains quietly unmoving in a dark spot during the bright\ndaylight hours. It does so because prolonged exposure to the\nsun causes its body to become slightly burned.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/41.png'),(42,'purple',0,50,90,'골뱃','Golbat','박쥐포켓몬','Bat Pokémon','생물의 혈액을 매우 좋아한다.\n특히 한밤중에 활동하는 경우가 많으며\n생피를 찾아 밤하늘을 날아다닌다.','Golbat loves to drink the blood of living things. It is particularly\nactive in the pitch black of night. This Pokémon flits around in\nthe night skies, seeking fresh blood.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/42.png'),(43,'blue',0,50,255,'뚜벅쵸','Oddish','잡초포켓몬','Weed Pokémon','낮에 땅속에 몸을 묻고\n땅의 영양을 전신으로 빨아올린다.\n비옥한 땅일수록 잎사귀에 윤이 난다고 한다.','During the daytime, Oddish buries itself in soil to absorb\nnutrients from the ground using its entire body.\nThe more fertile the soil, the glossier its leaves become.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/43.png'),(44,'blue',0,50,120,'냄새꼬','Gloom','잡초포켓몬','Weed Pokémon','위험을 느끼면 암술에서 내는 구린\n냄새가 더 강해지지만 마음이 평안할\n때는 구린 냄새를 내지 않는다.','Gloom releases a foul fragrance from the pistil of its flower.\nWhen faced with danger, the stench worsens.\nIf this Pokémon is feeling calm and secure, it does not\nrelease its usual stinky aroma.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/44.png'),(45,'red',0,50,45,'라플레시아','Vileplume','꽃포켓몬','Flower Pokémon','독 꽃가루는 심한 알레르기를 일으킨다.\n정글에서 아름다운 꽃을 발견해도\n섣불리 다가가지 않는 것이 좋다.','Vileplume’s toxic pollen triggers atrocious allergy attacks.\nThat’s why it is advisable never to approach any attractive\nflowers in a jungle, however pretty they may be.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/45.png'),(46,'red',0,70,190,'파라스','Paras','버섯포켓몬','Mushroom Pokémon','파라스로부터 양분을 빨아들여 자란\n버섯은 동충하초라고 불리고 있다.\n장수의 약이 되는 귀중한 버섯이다.','Paras has parasitic mushrooms growing on its back called\ntochukaso. They grow large by drawing nutrients from this\nBug Pokémon host. They are highly valued as a medicine\nfor extending life.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/46.png'),(47,'red',0,70,75,'파라섹트','Parasect','버섯포켓몬','Mushroom Pokémon','파라섹트는 집단으로 큰 나무의 밑동에\n붙어 영양을 빨아들인다.\n말라버리면 일제히 다른 나무로 이동한다.','Parasect is known to infest large trees en masse and drain\nnutrients from the lower trunk and roots. When an infested tree\ndies, they move onto another tree all at once.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/47.png'),(48,'purple',0,70,190,'콘팡','Venonat','곤충포켓몬','Insect Pokémon','몸을 지키기 위해 가늘고 딱딱한 털이\n전신을 둘러싸게 됐다고 전해진다.\n작은 먹잇감도 놓치지 않는 눈을 가졌다.','Venonat is said to have evolved with a coat of thin,\nstiff hair that covers its entire body for protection.\nIt possesses large eyes that never fail to spot even\nminuscule prey.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/48.png'),(49,'purple',0,70,75,'도나리','Venomoth','독나방포켓몬','Poison Moth Pokémon','야행성으로 밤에 활동을 시작한다.\n가로등 빛에 이끌려 모여든\n작은 벌레를 즐겨 먹는다.','Venomoth is nocturnal—it is a Pokémon that only becomes\nactive at night. Its favorite prey are small insects that gather\naround streetlights, attracted by the light in the darkness.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/49.png'),(50,'brown',0,50,255,'디그다','Diglett','두더지포켓몬','Mole Pokémon','농가 대부분이 디그다를 기르고 있다.\n디그다가 구멍을 판 땅은 적당히\n일궈져 있어 맛있는 채소가 재배되기 때문이다.','Diglett are raised in most farms. The reason is simple—\nwherever this Pokémon burrows, the soil is left perfectly tilled\nfor planting crops. This soil is made ideal for growing\ndelicious vegetables.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/50.png'),(51,'brown',0,50,50,'닥트리오','Dugtrio','두더지포켓몬','Mole Pokémon','본래 하나의 몸에서 세쌍둥이가\n된 것이라 모두 생각하는 것이 같다.\n힘을 모아 끝없이 파나간다.','Dugtrio are actually triplets that emerged from one body.\nAs a result, each triplet thinks exactly like the other\ntwo triplets. They work cooperatively to burrow endlessly.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/51.png'),(52,'yellow',0,50,255,'나옹','Meowth','요괴고양이포켓몬','Scratch Cat Pokémon','날카로운 발톱을 집어넣고 살금살금\n발소리를 내지 않고 걸을 수 있다.\n반짝반짝 빛나는 동전을 왠지 모르지만 매우 좋아한다.','Meowth withdraws its sharp claws into its paws to slinkily sneak\nabout without making any incriminating footsteps.\nFor some reason, this Pokémon loves shiny coins that\nglitter with light.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/52.png'),(53,'yellow',0,50,90,'페르시온','Persian','샴고양이포켓몬','Classy Cat Pokémon','튼튼한 6가닥의 수염은 공기의 움직임으로\n주변의 상태를 파악하는 역할을 한다.\n수염을 잡히면 얌전해진다.','Persian has six bold whiskers that give it a look of toughness.\nThe whiskers sense air movements to determine what is in the\nPokémon’s surrounding vicinity. It becomes docile if grabbed\nby the whiskers.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/53.png'),(54,'yellow',0,50,190,'고라파덕','Psyduck','오리포켓몬','Duck Pokémon','이상한 힘을 발휘하는 고라파덕에게서\n잠들어 있을 때만 발산되는 뇌파가\n관측되어 학회에서 화제가 되었다.','Psyduck uses a mysterious power. When it does so, this\nPokémon generates brain waves that are supposedly only seen\nin sleepers. This discovery spurred controversy\namong scholars.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/54.png'),(55,'blue',0,50,75,'골덕','Golduck','오리포켓몬','Duck Pokémon','손발의 물갈퀴와 유선형의 몸이\n수중에서 무서울 만큼 빠른 스피드를 낸다.\n금메달리스트보다 단연 빠르다.','The webbed flippers on its forelegs and hind legs and the\nstreamlined body of Golduck give it frightening speed.\nThis Pokémon is definitely much faster than even the most\nathletic swimmer.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/55.png'),(56,'brown',0,70,190,'망키','Mankey','돈숭이포켓몬','Pig Monkey Pokémon','몸이 떨리며 콧김이 거칠어지면\n화를 낼 조짐이지만 순식간에 격렬하게\n화를 내기 때문에 도망갈 틈이 없다.','When Mankey starts shaking and its nasal breathing turns\nrough, it’s a sure sign that it is becoming angry. However,\nbecause it goes into a towering rage almost instantly,\nit is impossible for anyone to flee its wrath.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/56.png'),(57,'brown',0,70,75,'성원숭','Primeape','돈숭이포켓몬','Pig Monkey Pokémon','격렬하게 화를 내면 혈액순환이\n좋아져 근육의 힘을 강하게 만든다.\n단 머리 회전은 느려진다.','When Primeape becomes furious, its blood circulation is\nboosted. In turn, its muscles are made even stronger.\nHowever, it also becomes much less intelligent at the\nsame time.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/57.png'),(58,'brown',0,50,190,'가디','Growlithe','강아지포켓몬','Puppy Pokémon','후각이 뛰어나서 한 번 맡은 냄새는\n무슨 일이 있어도 절대 잊지 않는다.\n상대의 기분을 냄새로 감지한다.','Growlithe has a superb sense of smell. Once it smells anything,\nthis Pokémon won’t forget the scent, no matter what. It uses\nits advanced olfactory sense to determine the emotions of\nother living things.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/58.png'),(59,'brown',0,50,75,'윈디','Arcanine','전설포켓몬','Legendary Pokémon','10000km 거리를 하루 만에 달려간다고\n전해지는 매우 빠른 포켓몬이다.\n체내에서 불타오르는 불꽃이 파워가 된다.','Arcanine is known for its high speed. It is said to be capable of\nrunning over 6,200 miles in a single day and night.\nThe fire that blazes wildly within this Pokémon’s body is its\nsource of power.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/59.png'),(60,'blue',0,50,255,'발챙이','Poliwag','올챙이포켓몬','Tadpole Pokémon','소용돌이 모양인 내장이 비칠 정도로\n얇은 피부이지만 날카로운 이빨을\n튕겨내는 탄력을 지니고 있다.','Poliwag has a very thin skin. It is possible to see the\nPokémon’s spiral innards right through the skin.\nDespite its thinness, however, the skin is also very flexible.\nEven sharp fangs bounce right off it.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/60.png'),(61,'blue',0,50,120,'슈륙챙이','Poliwhirl','올챙이포켓몬','Tadpole Pokémon','항상 몸의 표면이 액체로 미끈미끈하게\n젖어 있어서 적에게 붙잡혀도\n미끄덩 빠져나와 도망갈 수 있다.','The surface of Poliwhirl’s body is always wet and slick with\na slimy fluid. Because of this slippery covering, it can easily\nslip and slide out of the clutches of any enemy in battle.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/61.png'),(62,'blue',0,50,45,'강챙이','Poliwrath','올챙이포켓몬','Tadpole Pokémon','강인하게 발달한 근육은 아무리\n운동해도 지치는 일이 없다.\n태평양도 가볍게 횡단할 수 있을 정도다.','Poliwrath’s highly developed, brawny muscles never grow\nfatigued, however much it exercises. It is so tirelessly strong,\nthis Pokémon can swim back and forth across the ocean\nwithout effort.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/62.png'),(63,'brown',0,50,200,'캐이시','Abra','초능력포켓몬','Psi Pokémon','하루에 18시간 잠들어 있는 포켓몬이다.\n잠든 상태에서도 적의 기척을 감지하면\n순간이동하여 도망갈 수 있다.','Abra sleeps for eighteen hours a day. However, it can sense\nthe presence of foes even while it is sleeping. In such a\nsituation, this Pokémon immediately teleports to safety.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/63.png'),(64,'brown',0,50,100,'윤겔라','Kadabra','초능력포켓몬','Psi Pokémon','두통을 유발하는 특수한 알파파를\n발산하기 때문에 강한 정신력의 소유자가\n아니면 윤겔라의 트레이너가 될 수 없다.','Kadabra emits a peculiar alpha wave if it develops a headache.\nOnly those people with a particularly strong psyche can hope\nto become a Trainer of this Pokémon.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/64.png'),(65,'brown',0,50,50,'후딘','Alakazam','초능력포켓몬','Psi Pokémon','뇌가 점점 커져서 목으로는 지탱할 수\n없을 만큼 머리가 무거워졌다.\n초능력으로 머리를 지탱하고 있다.','Alakazam’s brain continually grows, making its head far too\nheavy to support with its neck. This Pokémon holds its head up\nusing its psychokinetic power instead.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/65.png'),(66,'gray',0,50,180,'알통몬','Machop','괴력포켓몬','Superpower Pokémon','아무리 운동을 해도 아프지 않은\n특별한 근육을 가진 포켓몬이다.\n어른 100명을 내던지는 파워다.','Machop’s muscles are special—they never get sore no matter\nhow much they are used in exercise. This Pokémon has\nsufficient power to hurl a hundred adult humans.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/66.png'),(67,'gray',0,50,90,'근육몬','Machoke','괴력포켓몬','Superpower Pokémon','잘 단련된 근육은 강철처럼 단단하다.\n씨름 선수의 몸을 손가락 1개로 쉽게\n들어 올릴 수 있는 괴력의 포켓몬이다.','Machoke’s thoroughly toned muscles possess the hardness\nof steel. This Pokémon has so much strength, it can easily\nhold aloft a sumo wrestler on just one finger.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/67.png'),(68,'gray',0,50,45,'괴력몬','Machamp','괴력포켓몬','Superpower Pokémon','무엇이든 내던질 수 있는 파워를 지녔으나\n세밀한 작업을 하면 팔이 얽히고 만다.\n생각하기보다 몸이 먼저 움직인다.','Machamp has the power to hurl anything aside. However,\ntrying to do any work requiring care and dexterity causes its\narms to get tangled. This Pokémon tends to leap into action\nbefore it thinks.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/68.png'),(69,'green',0,70,255,'모다피','Bellsprout','꽃포켓몬','Flower Pokémon','가늘고 유연한 몸은 아무리 강한\n공격이라도 휘어져 피할 수 있다.\n입에서 철도 녹일 수 있는 액체가 나온다.','Bellsprout’s thin and flexible body lets it bend and sway to\navoid any attack, however strong it may be. From its mouth,\nthis Pokémon spits a corrosive fluid that melts even iron.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/69.png'),(70,'green',0,70,120,'우츠동','Weepinbell','파리잡이포켓몬','Flycatcher Pokémon','밤이 되면 엉덩이의 갈고리를 나뭇가지에\n걸고 매달려서 잠든다.\n잠버릇이 나쁘면 아침에 떨어져 있다.','Weepinbell has a large hook on its rear end. At night, the\nPokémon hooks on to a tree branch and goes to sleep.\nIf it moves around in its sleep, it may wake up to find itself\non the ground.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/70.png'),(71,'green',0,70,45,'우츠보트','Victreebel','파리잡이포켓몬','Flycatcher Pokémon','머리에 달린 긴 덩굴을 작은\n생물처럼 움직여서 먹이를 유인한다.\n가까이 왔을 때 덥석 한 번에 삼킨다.','Victreebel has a long vine that extends from its head.\nThis vine is waved and flicked about as if it were an animal to\nattract prey. When an unsuspecting prey draws near, this\nPokémon swallows it whole.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/71.png'),(72,'blue',0,50,190,'왕눈해','Tentacool','해파리포켓몬','Jellyfish Pokémon','몸 대부분이 물로 되어 있어\n바다에서 나오면 바싹 말라버린다.\n말라버렸을 때는 바다로 돌려보내 주자.','Tentacool’s body is largely composed of water. If it is removed\nfrom the sea, it dries up like parchment. If this Pokémon\nhappens to become dehydrated, put it back into the sea.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/72.png'),(73,'blue',0,50,60,'독파리','Tentacruel','해파리포켓몬','Jellyfish Pokémon','머리의 붉은 구슬이 반짝일 때 격렬한\n초음파가 주변에 발사된다.\n그때 바다가 격렬히 파도친다고 한다.','Tentacruel has large red orbs on its head. The orbs glow\nbefore lashing the vicinity with a harsh ultrasonic blast.\nThis Pokémon’s outburst creates rough waves around it.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/73.png'),(74,'brown',0,70,255,'꼬마돌','Geodude','암석포켓몬','Rock Pokémon','오래 산 꼬마돌일수록 몸의 모난 부분이\n깎여 둥그렇게 되지만 마음은 언제까지나\n울퉁불퉁 뾰족하고 거칠다.','The longer a Geodude lives, the more its edges are chipped\nand worn away, making it more rounded in appearance.\nHowever, this Pokémon’s heart will remain hard, craggy,\nand rough always.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/74.png'),(75,'brown',0,70,120,'데구리','Graveler','암석포켓몬','Rock Pokémon','바위를 먹고 성장하는 포켓몬이다.\n이끼가 낀 바위를 좋아하는 것 같다.\n하루에 1톤의 바위를 먹어버린다.','Graveler grows by feeding on rocks. Apparently, it prefers to\neat rocks that are covered in moss. This Pokémon eats its way\nthrough a ton of rocks on a daily basis.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/75.png'),(76,'brown',0,70,45,'딱구리','Golem','메가톤포켓몬','Megaton Pokémon','큰 지진이 일어나면 산에 사는 딱구리\n여러 마리가 산기슭까지 데굴데굴\n굴러 내려오는 일이 있다.','Golem live up on mountains. If there is a large earthquake,\nthese Pokémon will come rolling down off the mountains\nen masse to the foothills below.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/76.png'),(77,'yellow',0,50,190,'포니타','Ponyta','불의말포켓몬','Fire Horse Pokémon','막 태어나서는 겨우 설 수 있는 정도지만\n넘어지면서 부모의 뒤를 쫓아다니는\n동안 하반신이 튼튼하게 자라난다.','Ponyta is very weak at birth. It can barely stand up.\nThis Pokémon becomes stronger by stumbling and falling to\nkeep up with its parent.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/77.png'),(78,'yellow',0,50,60,'날쌩마','Rapidash','불의말포켓몬','Fire Horse Pokémon','평상시는 느긋하게 들판을 뛰어다니지만\n한 번 마음먹으면 갈기의 불꽃을\n불태우며 시속 240km로 달린다.','Rapidash usually can be seen casually cantering in the\nfields and plains. However, when this Pokémon turns serious,\nits fiery manes flare and blaze as it gallops its way up to\n150 mph.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/78.png'),(79,'pink',0,50,190,'야돈','Slowpoke','얼간이포켓몬','Dopey Pokémon','꼬리를 강에 넣고 먹이를 낚지만\n이윽고 무엇을 하고 있었는지 잊고\n강변에 엎드려 누운 채로 하루를 보낸다.','Slowpoke uses its tail to catch prey by dipping it in water at\nthe side of a river. However, this Pokémon often forgets what\nit’s doing and often spends entire days just loafing at\nwater’s edge.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/79.png'),(80,'pink',0,50,75,'야도란','Slowbro','기생포켓몬','Hermit Crab Pokémon','셀러가 물고 있어서 꼬리로 먹이를\n낚을 수 없게 된 야도란은 마지못해\n물속을 헤엄쳐 먹이를 잡고 있다.','Slowbro’s tail has a Shellder firmly attached with a bite.\nAs a result, the tail can’t be used for fishing anymore.\nThis causes Slowbro to grudgingly swim and catch\nprey instead.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/80.png'),(81,'gray',0,50,190,'코일','Magnemite','자석포켓몬','Magnet Pokémon','전선에 들러붙어 전기를 먹고 있다.\n정전되면 누전차단기를 살펴보자.\n코일이 빽빽이 들러붙어 있을지도 모른다.','Magnemite attaches itself to power lines to feed on electricity.\nIf your house has a power outage, check your circuit breakers.\nYou may find a large number of this Pokémon clinging to the\nbreaker box.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/81.png'),(82,'gray',0,50,60,'레어코일','Magneton','자석포켓몬','Magnet Pokémon','강한 자력으로 기계를 망가트리기 때문에\n큰 마을에서는 사이렌을 울려\n레어코일의 대량 발생을 알린다.','Magneton emits a powerful magnetic force that is fatal to\nmechanical devices. As a result, large cities sound sirens\nto warn citizens of large-scale outbreaks of this Pokémon.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/82.png'),(83,'brown',0,50,45,'파오리','Farfetch’d','청둥오리포켓몬','Wild Duck Pokémon','가지고 있는 식물의 줄기에도 좋은 것과\n그렇지 않은 것이 있는 듯하여 파오리들이\n줄기를 둘러싸고 싸우는 일도 있다.','Farfetch’d is always seen with a stalk from a plant of some\nsort. Apparently, there are good stalks and bad stalks. This\nPokémon has been known to fight with others over stalks.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/83.png'),(84,'brown',0,70,190,'두두','Doduo','쌍둥이새포켓몬','Twin Bird Pokémon','2개의 머리가 동시에 잠드는 일은 없다.\n자고 있을 때 적에게 습격당하지 않도록\n교대로 망을 보고 있기 때문이다.','Doduo’s two heads never sleep at the same time. Its two\nheads take turns sleeping, so one head can always keep\nwatch for enemies while the other one sleeps.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/84.png'),(85,'brown',0,70,45,'두트리오','Dodrio','세쌍둥이새포켓몬','Triple Bird Pokémon','3개의 머리가 서로 다른 방향을\n향하고 있을 때는 경계 중인 증거다.\n섣불리 가까이 가면 부리에 쪼인다.','Watch out if Dodrio’s three heads are looking in three separate\ndirections. It’s a sure sign that it is on its guard. Don’t go near\nthis Pokémon if it’s being wary—it may decide to peck you.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/85.png'),(86,'white',0,70,190,'쥬쥬','Seel','강치포켓몬','Sea Lion Pokémon','얼음으로 뒤덮인 바다에서 먹이를 잡는다.\n숨을 쉴 때는 머리의 돌출된 부분으로\n얼음을 깨고 바다 밖으로 얼굴을 내민다.','Seel hunts for prey in the frigid sea underneath sheets of ice.\nWhen it needs to breathe, it punches a hole through the ice\nwith the sharply protruding section of its head.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/86.png'),(87,'white',0,70,75,'쥬레곤','Dewgong','강치포켓몬','Sea Lion Pokémon','차가운 얼음 위에서 자는 것을 매우 좋아한다.\n옛날에 빙산에서 자는 모습을 본\n뱃사람이 인어로 착각했다.','Dewgong loves to snooze on bitterly cold ice. The sight of this\nPokémon sleeping on a glacier was mistakenly thought to be a\nmermaid by a mariner long ago.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/87.png'),(88,'purple',0,70,190,'질퍽이','Grimer','진흙포켓몬','Sludge Pokémon','흐물흐물 물렁물렁한 몸은 아무리\n좁은 틈이라도 파고들어 갈 수 있다.\n하수관에 들어가 지저분한 물을 마신다.','Grimer’s sludgy and rubbery body can be forced through any\nopening, however small it may be. This Pokémon enters sewer\npipes to drink filthy wastewater.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/88.png'),(89,'purple',0,70,75,'질뻐기','Muk','진흙포켓몬','Sludge Pokémon','몸에서 배어 나오는 체액은 코를\n찌를 정도로 강렬한 냄새를 뿜는다.\n한 방울로 수영장의 물이 탁해지고 냄새가 난다.','From Muk’s body seeps a foul fluid that gives off a\nnose-bendingly horrible stench. Just one drop of this\nPokémon’s body fluid can turn a pool stagnant and rancid.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/89.png'),(90,'purple',0,50,190,'셀러','Shellder','두조개포켓몬','Bivalve Pokémon','밤이 되면 큰 혀로 해저의\n모래에 구멍을 뚫고 그 안에서 잔다.\n혀를 내민 채로 껍질을 닫고 잠든다.','At night, this Pokémon uses its broad tongue to burrow a hole\nin the seafloor sand and then sleep in it. While it is sleeping,\nShellder closes its shell, but leaves its tongue hanging out.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/90.png'),(91,'purple',0,50,60,'파르셀','Cloyster','두조개포켓몬','Bivalve Pokémon','들이마신 바닷물을 뒤쪽으로 기운차게\n뿜어내서 바닷속을 헤엄친다.\n같은 방법으로 가시도 발사한다.','Cloyster is capable of swimming in the sea. It does so by\nswallowing water, then jetting it out toward the rear.\nThis Pokémon shoots spikes from its shell using the\nsame system.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/91.png'),(92,'purple',0,50,190,'고오스','Gastly','가스포켓몬','Gas Pokémon','강풍을 맞으면 가스로 된 몸은\n금세 날려져서 작아진다.\n바람을 피해 고오스가 처마 밑에 모인다.','Gastly is largely composed of gaseous matter. When exposed\nto a strong wind, the gaseous body quickly dwindles away.\nGroups of this Pokémon cluster under the eaves of houses to\nescape the ravages of wind.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/92.png'),(93,'purple',0,50,90,'고우스트','Haunter','가스포켓몬','Gas Pokémon','어둠 속에서 나타나는 고우스트가 손짓으로\n불러도 절대 가까이 가면 안 된다.\n날름 핥아져 생명을 빨린다.','Haunter is a dangerous Pokémon. If one beckons you while\nfloating in darkness, you must never approach it. This Pokémon\nwill try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/93.png'),(94,'purple',0,50,45,'팬텀','Gengar','그림자포켓몬','Shadow Pokémon','한밤중 가로등 빛에 생겨난 그림자가\n자신을 앞질러 가는 것은 팬텀이\n그림자인 척하며 뛰어가기 때문이다.','Sometimes, on a dark night, your shadow thrown by a\nstreetlight will suddenly and startlingly overtake you.\nIt is actually a Gengar running past you, pretending to be\nyour shadow.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/94.png'),(95,'gray',0,50,45,'롱스톤','Onix','돌뱀포켓몬','Rock Snake Pokémon','뇌에 자석이 있어서 땅속을\n파고 나가도 방향을 틀리지 않는다.\n나이를 먹을수록 몸이 둥그스름해진다.','Onix has a magnet in its brain. It acts as a compass so that this\nPokémon does not lose direction while it is tunneling.\nAs it grows older, its body becomes increasingly rounder\nand smoother.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/95.png'),(96,'yellow',0,70,190,'슬리프','Drowzee','최면포켓몬','Hypnosis Pokémon','잠들었을 때 너의 코가 근질근질하다면\n슬리프가 머리맡에 서서 콧구멍을\n통해 꿈을 먹으려고 하는 신호다.','If your nose becomes itchy while you are sleeping, it’s a sure\nsign that one of these Pokémon is standing above your pillow\nand trying to eat your dream through your nostrils.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/96.png'),(97,'yellow',0,70,75,'슬리퍼','Hypno','최면포켓몬','Hypnosis Pokémon','손에 쥐고 있는 추의 움직임과 반짝임이\n상대를 깊은 최면 상태에 빠트린다.\n먹이를 찾으며 추를 손질하고 있다.','Hypno holds a pendulum in its hand. The arcing movement and\nglitter of the pendulum lull the foe into a deep state of\nhypnosis. While this Pokémon searches for prey, it polishes\nthe pendulum.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/97.png'),(98,'red',0,50,225,'크랩','Krabby','게포켓몬','River Crab Pokémon','모래 해변에 구멍을 뚫고 거기서 살고 있다.\n먹이가 적은 모래 해변에서는 자리 확보를\n위해 다투는 크랩들을 볼 수 있다.','Krabby live on beaches, burrowed inside holes dug into the\nsand. On sandy beaches with little in the way of food, these\nPokémon can be seen squabbling with each other\nover territory.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/98.png'),(99,'red',0,50,60,'킹크랩','Kingler','집게포켓몬','Pincer Pokémon','킹크랩은 거대한 집게를 휘둘러\n동료 간에 신호를 보내지만\n집게가 무거워서 곧 지쳐버린다.','Kingler has an enormous, oversized claw. It waves this huge\nclaw in the air to communicate with others. However, because\nthe claw is so heavy, the Pokémon quickly tires.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/99.png'),(100,'red',0,70,190,'찌리리공','Voltorb','볼포켓몬','Ball Pokémon','몬스터볼을 만드는 회사에서\n처음 발견됐다는 점과 생김새가 비슷한\n점의 관련성은 아직도 수수께끼다.','Voltorb was first sighted at a company that manufactures\nPoké Balls. The link between that sighting and the fact\nthat this Pokémon looks very similar to a Poké Ball remains\na mystery.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/100.png'),(101,'red',0,70,60,'붐볼','Electrode','볼포켓몬','Ball Pokémon','공기 중의 전기 에너지를 먹는다.\n번개가 치는 날에는 전기를 너무 먹은\n붐볼이 이곳저곳에서 대폭발한다.','Electrode eats electricity in the atmosphere. On days when\nlightning strikes, you can see this Pokémon exploding all over\nthe place from eating too much electricity.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/101.png'),(102,'pink',0,50,90,'아라리','Exeggcute','알포켓몬','Egg Pokémon','동료애가 강한 여섯 알은 서로\n끌어당기며 빙글빙글 회전하고 있다.\n껍질의 금이 늘어나면 진화가 가까워진 것.','This Pokémon consists of six eggs that form a closely knit\ncluster. The six eggs attract each other and spin around.\nWhen cracks increasingly appear on the eggs, Exeggcute is\nclose to evolution.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/102.png'),(103,'yellow',0,50,45,'나시','Exeggutor','야자열매포켓몬','Coconut Pokémon','남쪽 나라 태생인 나시의 머리는 강한\n햇빛을 잔뜩 받고 점점 자라\n땅에 떨어지면 아라리가 된다고 한다.','Exeggutor originally came from the tropics. Its heads\nsteadily grow larger from exposure to strong sunlight.\nIt is said that when the heads fall off, they group together\nto form Exeggcute.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/103.png'),(104,'brown',0,50,190,'탕구리','Cubone','고독포켓몬','Lonely Pokémon','두 번 다시 만나지 못하는 어미의 모습을\n보름달에서 발견하고 울음소리를 낸다.\n뒤집어쓰고 있는 뼈의 얼룩은 눈물 자국이다.','Cubone pines for the mother it will never see again.\nSeeing a likeness of its mother in the full moon, it cries.\nThe stains on the skull the Pokémon wears are made by the\ntears it sheds.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/104.png'),(105,'brown',0,50,75,'텅구리','Marowak','뼈다귀포켓몬','Bone Keeper Pokémon','어미를 만날 수 없는 슬픔을 극복한\n탕구리가 늠름하게 진화한 모습이다.\n단련된 마음은 간단히 꺾이지 않는다.','Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has overcome\nits sadness at the loss of its mother and grown tough.\nThis Pokémon’s tempered and hardened spirit is not\neasily broken.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/105.png'),(106,'brown',0,50,45,'시라소몬','Hitmonlee','킥포켓몬','Kicking Pokémon','자유롭게 신축되는 다리로 강렬한\n킥을 날려 상대를 발로 차 쓰러트린다.\n싸운 뒤에 지친 다리를 주물러 풀어준다.','Hitmonlee’s legs freely contract and stretch. Using these\nspringlike legs, it bowls over foes with devastating kicks.\nAfter battle, it rubs down its legs and loosens the muscles to\novercome fatigue.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/106.png'),(107,'brown',0,50,45,'홍수몬','Hitmonchan','펀치포켓몬','Punching Pokémon','세계 챔피언을 목표했던 복서의\n혼이 깃들었다고 하는 홍수몬은\n불굴의 정신으로 절대 지쳐 쓰러지지 않는다.','Hitmonchan is said to possess the spirit of a boxer who had\nbeen working toward a world championship. This Pokémon has\nan indomitable spirit and will never give up in the face\nof adversity.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/107.png'),(108,'pink',0,50,45,'내루미','Lickitung','핥기포켓몬','Licking Pokémon','처음 본 것은 반드시 핥아본다.\n혀의 감촉과 맛으로 기억해두는 것이다.\n하지만 시큼한 것을 핥는 것은 조금 꺼린다.','Whenever Lickitung comes across something new, it will\nunfailingly give it a lick. It does so because it memorizes things\nby texture and by taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/108.png'),(109,'purple',0,50,190,'또가스','Koffing','독가스포켓몬','Poison Gas Pokémon','자극받으면 가스의 독소가 강해져\n몸의 이곳저곳에서 강하게 내뿜는다.\n동그랗게 부풀어 오른 후 대폭발한다.','If Koffing becomes agitated, it raises the toxicity of its internal\ngases and jets them out from all over its body. This Pokémon\nmay also overinflate its round body, then explode.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/109.png'),(110,'purple',0,50,60,'또도가스','Weezing','독가스포켓몬','Poison Gas Pokémon','부패한 음식물 쓰레기에서 나온 가스를 매우 좋아한다.\n청소하지 않는 집에서 눌러살며 가족이\n모두 잠든 한밤중에 쓰레기통을 뒤진다.','Weezing loves the gases given off by rotted kitchen garbage.\nThis Pokémon will find a dirty, unkempt house and make it its\nhome. At night, when the people in the house are asleep, it will\ngo through the trash.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/110.png'),(111,'gray',0,50,120,'뿔카노','Rhyhorn','뿔포켓몬','Spikes Pokémon','오로지 곧장 돌진하여 부순다.\n강철 덩어리에 부딪혀도 멀쩡하지만\n하루가 지나면 아픔을 조금 느낀다.','Rhyhorn runs in a straight line, smashing everything in its path.\nIt is not bothered even if it rushes headlong into a block of\nsteel. This Pokémon may feel some pain from the collision the\nnext day, however.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/111.png'),(112,'gray',0,50,60,'코뿌리','Rhydon','드릴포켓몬','Drill Pokémon','뿔은 다이아몬드 원석을 부수고\n꼬리의 일격은 빌딩을 쓰러트린다.\n단단한 피부는 대포에도 상처 입지 않는다.','Rhydon’s horn can crush even uncut diamonds. One sweeping\nblow of its tail can topple a building. This Pokémon’s hide is\nextremely tough. Even direct cannon hits don’t leave a scratch.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/112.png'),(113,'pink',0,140,30,'럭키','Chansey','알포켓몬','Egg Pokémon','영양 만점인 알을 매일 낳는다.\n식욕을 잃은 사람도 한 번에\n먹어치울 정도로 맛있는 알이다.','Chansey lays nutritionally excellent eggs on an everyday basis.\nThe eggs are so delicious, they are easily and eagerly\ndevoured by even those people who have lost their appetite.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/113.png'),(114,'blue',0,50,45,'덩쿠리','Tangela','넝쿨포켓몬','Vine Pokémon','적에게 붙잡히면 덩굴이 뚝 하고 끊긴다.\n전혀 아프지 않기 때문에 그 틈에 도망간다.\n다음 날에는 새로운 덩굴이 자란다.','Tangela’s vines snap off easily if they are grabbed.\nThis happens without pain, allowing it to make a quick\ngetaway. The lost vines are replaced by newly grown vines the\nvery next day.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/114.png'),(115,'brown',0,50,45,'캥카','Kangaskhan','가족포켓몬','Parent Pokémon','캥카의 새끼가 혼자서 놀고 있어도\n절대로 잡으려 하면 안 된다.\n가까이 있는 부모가 격렬히 화낸다.','If you come across a young Kangaskhan playing by itself, you\nmust never disturb it or attempt to catch it. The baby\nPokémon’s parent is sure to be in the area, and it will become\nviolently enraged at you.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/115.png'),(116,'blue',0,50,225,'쏘드라','Horsea','드래곤포켓몬','Dragon Pokémon','작은 벌레나 바위의 이끼를 먹는다.\n해류가 빨라지면 꼬리로 바위나\n산호를 휘감아 떠내려가지 않게 한다.','Horsea eats small insects and moss off of rocks. If the ocean\ncurrent turns fast, this Pokémon anchors itself by wrapping its\ntail around rocks or coral to prevent being washed away.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/116.png'),(117,'blue',0,50,75,'시드라','Seadra','드래곤포켓몬','Dragon Pokémon','산호 가지 사이로 들어가 잠잔다.\n시드라가 있는 줄 모르고 산호를\n잡으려다 독가시에 찔리곤 한다.','Seadra sleeps after wriggling itself between the branches of\ncoral. Those trying to harvest coral are occasionally stung by\nthis Pokémon’s poison barbs if they fail to notice it.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/117.png'),(118,'red',0,50,225,'콘치','Goldeen','금붕어포켓몬','Goldfish Pokémon','물속에서 우아하게 나부끼는 지느러미가 매우\n아름다운 포켓몬이지만 방심하고 있으면\n강렬한 뿔의 일격을 당한다.','Goldeen is a very beautiful Pokémon with fins that billow\nelegantly in water. However, don’t let your guard down around\nthis Pokémon—it could ram you powerfully with its horn.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/118.png'),(119,'red',0,50,60,'왕콘치','Seaking','금붕어포켓몬','Goldfish Pokémon','가을이 되면 암컷에게 프러포즈하기 위해\n강바닥에서 춤추는 수컷을 볼 수 있다.\n몸의 색이 가장 아름다운 계절이다.','In the autumn, Seaking males can be seen performing\ncourtship dances in riverbeds to woo females. During this\nseason, this Pokémon’s body coloration is at its most beautiful.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/119.png'),(120,'brown',0,50,225,'별가사리','Staryu','별포켓몬','Star Shape Pokémon','여름이 끝날 무렵 밤에 모래 해변에 가면\n핵이라고 불리는 기관을 붉게 빛내는\n별가사리가 별처럼 보인다.','Staryu’s center section has an organ called the core that\nshines bright red. If you go to a beach toward the end of\nsummer, the glowing cores of these Pokémon look like the\nstars in the sky.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/120.png'),(121,'purple',0,50,60,'아쿠스타','Starmie','수수께끼포켓몬','Mysterious Pokémon','몸의 중심에 있는 핵이라 불리는\n부분이 일곱 빛깔로 빛나기에\n바다의 보석이라는 별명이 붙었다.','Starmie’s center section—the core—glows brightly in seven\ncolors. Because of its luminous nature, this Pokémon has\nbeen given the nickname “the gem of the sea.”','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/121.png'),(122,'pink',0,50,45,'마임맨','Mr. Mime','배리어포켓몬','Barrier Pokémon','몸짓으로 눈에 보이지 않는 것이 그곳에\n있다고 믿게 만드는 팬터마임의 달인이다.\n있다고 믿게 만든 것은 정말로 나타난다.','Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. Its gestures and motions\nconvince watchers that something unseeable actually exists.\nOnce the watchers are convinced, the unseeable thing exists\nas if it were real.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/122.png'),(123,'green',0,50,45,'스라크','Scyther','버마재비포켓몬','Mantis Pokémon','눈에 보이지 않는 빠른 스피드가 양팔에\n달린 낫의 날카로움을 한층 높여준다.\n한 번 휘두르면 큰 나무도 두 동강 난다.','Scyther is blindingly fast. Its blazing speed enhances the\neffectiveness of the twin scythes on its forearms.\nThis Pokémon’s scythes are so effective, they can slice\nthrough thick logs in one wicked stroke.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/123.png'),(124,'red',0,50,45,'루주라','Jynx','인간형태포켓몬','Human Shape Pokémon','춤추는 듯한 자세로 리드미컬하게 걷는다.\n그 움직임은 보고 있는 사람마저 얼떨결에\n허리를 흔들 정도로 경쾌하다.','Jynx walks rhythmically, swaying and shaking its hips as if it\nwere dancing. Its motions are so bouncingly alluring, people\nseeing it are compelled to shake their hips without giving any\nthought to what they are doing.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/124.png'),(125,'yellow',0,50,45,'에레브','Electabuzz','전기포켓몬','Electric Pokémon','폭풍이 오면 나무 위처럼 벼락이\n떨어질 만한 높은 장소로 앞다투어 올라간다.\n피뢰침 대용으로 삼는 마을도 있다.','When a storm arrives, gangs of this Pokémon compete with\neach other to scale heights that are likely to be stricken by\nlightning bolts. Some towns use Electabuzz in place of\nlightning rods.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/125.png'),(126,'red',0,50,45,'마그마','Magmar','불뿜기포켓몬','Spitfire Pokémon','싸우게 되면 몸에서 작열하는\n불꽃을 뿜어내 상대를 위협한다.\n그 열풍으로 주변의 초목도 불태운다.','In battle, Magmar blows out intensely hot flames from all\nover its body to intimidate its opponent. This Pokémon’s\nfiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees\nin its surroundings.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/126.png'),(127,'brown',0,50,45,'쁘사이저','Pinsir','뿔집게포켓몬','Stag Beetle Pokémon','자신의 몸무게 두 배나 되는 상대를 뿔로\n집어 가볍게 들어 올리는 괴력을 지녔다.\n추운 곳에서는 몸의 움직임이 둔해진다.','Pinsir is astoundingly strong. It can grip a foe weighing twice\nits weight in its horns and easily lift it. This Pokémon’s\nmovements turn sluggish in cold places.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/127.png'),(128,'brown',0,50,45,'켄타로스','Tauros','성난소포켓몬','Wild Bull Pokémon','항상 날뛰지 않으면 성에 차지 않는다.\n싸울 상대가 없을 때는 큰 나무를\n들이받아 쓰러트리고 맘을 가라앉힌다.','This Pokémon is not satisfied unless it is rampaging at all\ntimes. If there is no opponent for Tauros to battle, it will\ncharge at thick trees and knock them down to calm itself.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/128.png'),(129,'red',0,50,255,'잉어킹','Magikarp','물고기포켓몬','Fish Pokémon','튀어 오르기만 하는 한심한 포켓몬이다.\n왜 튀어 오르는지 조사한 연구자가\n있을 정도로 무조건 튀고 튀고 튀어 오르기만 한다.','Magikarp is a pathetic excuse for a Pokémon that is only\ncapable of flopping and splashing. This behavior prompted\nscientists to undertake research into it.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/129.png'),(130,'blue',0,50,45,'갸라도스','Gyarados','흉악포켓몬','Atrocious Pokémon','잉어킹에서 갸라도스로 진화할 때\n뇌세포의 구조가 재구성되기 때문에\n성격이 난폭해진다고 전해진다.','When Magikarp evolves into Gyarados, its brain cells undergo a\nstructural transformation. It is said that this transformation is to\nblame for this Pokémon’s wildly violent nature.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/130.png'),(131,'blue',0,50,45,'라프라스','Lapras','탈것포켓몬','Transport Pokémon','사람이 멸종의 위기로 몰아갔다.\n석양이 내리면 수가 줄어든 동료를\n찾아 슬픈 목소리로 노래한다고 한다.','People have driven Lapras almost to the point of extinction.\nIn the evenings, this Pokémon is said to sing plaintively as it\nseeks what few others of its kind still remain.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/131.png'),(132,'purple',0,50,35,'메타몽','Ditto','변신포켓몬','Transform Pokémon','몸의 세포를 재구성하여 변신한다.\n전에 봤던 것을 기억해내면서 바뀌면\n조금 다른 형태가 되어버린다.','Ditto rearranges its cell structure to transform itself into other\nshapes. However, if it tries to transform itself into something\nby relying on its memory, this Pokémon manages to get\ndetails wrong.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/132.png'),(133,'brown',0,50,45,'이브이','Eevee','진화포켓몬','Evolution Pokémon','사는 환경에 따라 돌연변이하는\n불안정한 유전자를 지닌 포켓몬이다.\n돌의 방사선이 진화를 일으킨다.','Eevee has an unstable genetic makeup that suddenly mutates\ndue to the environment in which it lives. Radiation from various\nstones causes this Pokémon to evolve.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/133.png'),(134,'blue',0,50,45,'샤미드','Vaporeon','거품뿜기포켓몬','Bubble Jet Pokémon','돌연변이로 인해 물속에서 생활할 수\n있도록 지느러미와 아가미가 생겨났다.\n물을 자유로이 조종하는 힘을 지녔다.','Vaporeon underwent a spontaneous mutation and grew fins\nand gills that allow it to live underwater. This Pokémon has the\nability to freely control water.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/134.png'),(135,'yellow',0,50,45,'쥬피썬더','Jolteon','번개포켓몬','Lightning Pokémon','세포에서 나오는 약한 전기를 털의\n정전기로 증폭시켜 번개를 떨어트린다.\n곤두세운 털은 전기를 띤 바늘이다.','Jolteon’s cells generate a low level of electricity. This power is\namplified by the static electricity of its fur, enabling the\nPokémon to drop thunderbolts. The bristling fur is made of\nelectrically charged needles.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/135.png'),(136,'red',0,50,45,'부스터','Flareon','불꽃포켓몬','Flame Pokémon','푹신한 털은 높이 오른 체온을\n공기 중으로 발산하여 낮추는 기능을 지녔다.\n체온은 최고 900도까지 올라간다.','Flareon’s fluffy fur has a functional purpose—it releases heat\ninto the air so that its body does not get excessively hot.\nThis Pokémon’s body temperature can rise to a maximum of\n1,650 degrees Fahrenheit.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/136.png'),(137,'pink',0,50,45,'폴리곤','Porygon','가상포켓몬','Virtual Pokémon','전신을 프로그램 데이터로 되돌려\n전자 공간에 들어갈 수 있다.\n복사 방지가 되어 있어 복사할 수 없다.','Porygon is capable of reverting itself entirely back to program\ndata and entering cyberspace. This Pokémon is copy protected\nso it cannot be duplicated by copying.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/137.png'),(138,'blue',0,50,45,'암나이트','Omanyte','소용돌이포켓몬','Spiral Pokémon','오랜 옛날에 멸종됐지만 인간의 손으로\n화석에서 부활시킨 포켓몬 중 하나다.\n적에게 습격당하면 단단한 껍질 속에 숨는다.','Omanyte is one of the ancient and long-since-extinct Pokémon\nthat have been regenerated from fossils by people. If attacked\nby an enemy, it withdraws itself inside its hard shell.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/138.png'),(139,'blue',0,50,45,'암스타','Omastar','소용돌이포켓몬','Spiral Pokémon','촉수를 이용하여 먹이를 잡는다.\n껍질이 너무 커진 탓에 움직임이\n둔해져서 멸종했다고 여겨지고 있다.','Omastar uses its tentacles to capture its prey. It is believed to\nhave become extinct because its shell grew too large and\nheavy, causing its movements to become too slow\nand ponderous.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/139.png'),(140,'brown',0,50,45,'투구','Kabuto','껍질포켓몬','Shellfish Pokémon','화석에서 부활한 포켓몬이지만 드물게\n살아 있는 투구를 발견할 수 있다.\n그 모습은 3억 년 동안 변치 않았다.','Kabuto is a Pokémon that has been regenerated from a fossil.\nHowever, in extremely rare cases, living examples have been\ndiscovered. The Pokémon has not changed at all for\n300 million years.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/140.png'),(141,'brown',0,50,45,'투구푸스','Kabutops','껍질포켓몬','Shellfish Pokémon','물속을 헤엄쳐 먹이를 잡았었다.\n물에서의 생활을 지나 땅에서 살 수 있도록\n아가미나 다리 등이 변화되기 시작했다.','Kabutops swam underwater to hunt for its prey in ancient\ntimes. The Pokémon was apparently evolving from being a\nwater dweller to living on land as evident from the beginnings\nof change in its gills and legs.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/141.png'),(142,'purple',0,50,45,'프테라','Aerodactyl','화석포켓몬','Fossil Pokémon','호박에서 추출한 유전자를 재생하여\n부활한 공룡시대의 포켓몬이다.\n하늘의 왕이었다고 상상된다.','Aerodactyl is a Pokémon from the age of dinosaurs. It was\nregenerated from genetic material extracted from amber. It is\nimagined to have been the king of the skies in ancient times.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/142.png'),(143,'black',0,50,25,'잠만보','Snorlax','졸음포켓몬','Sleeping Pokémon','먹고 자는 것을 반복하다 하루가 끝난다.\n큰 배 위를 놀이터로 삼은 아이들이\n있을 정도로 얌전한 포켓몬이다.','Snorlax’s typical day consists of nothing more than eating and\nsleeping. It is such a docile Pokémon that there are children\nwho use its expansive belly as a place to play.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/143.png'),(144,'blue',1,35,3,'프리져','Articuno','냉동포켓몬','Freeze Pokémon','얼음을 조종하는 전설의 새포켓몬이다.\n날갯짓하면 공기가 차갑게 식기 때문에\n프리져가 날면 눈이 온다고 전해진다.','Articuno is a legendary bird Pokémon that can control ice.\nThe flapping of its wings chills the air. As a result, it is said\nthat when this Pokémon flies, snow will fall.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/144.png'),(145,'yellow',1,35,3,'썬더','Zapdos','전기포켓몬','Electric Pokémon','전기를 조종하는 전설의 새포켓몬이다.\n평상시는 번개 구름 속에서 지낸다.\n번개를 맞으면 힘이 솟아난다.','Zapdos is a legendary bird Pokémon that has the ability to\ncontrol electricity. It usually lives in thunderclouds.\nThe Pokémon gains power if it is stricken by lightning bolts.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/145.png'),(146,'yellow',1,35,3,'파이어','Moltres','화염포켓몬','Flame Pokémon','불꽃을 조종하는 전설의 새포켓몬이다.\n몸이 상처 입으면 분화구의 마그마에 들어가\n전신을 불태워 상처를 치료한다고 한다.','Moltres is a legendary bird Pokémon that has the ability to\ncontrol fire. If this Pokémon is injured, it is said to dip its body\nin the molten magma of a volcano to burn and heal itself.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/146.png'),(147,'blue',0,35,45,'미뇽','Dratini','드래곤포켓몬','Dragon Pokémon','미뇽이 탈피를 반복하는 것은\n몸속에서 생명 에너지가 점점 부풀어\n올라 억제할 수 없게 되기 때문이다.','Dratini continually molts and sloughs off its old skin. It does so\nbecause the life energy within its body steadily builds to reach\nuncontrollable levels.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/147.png'),(148,'blue',0,35,45,'신뇽','Dragonair','드래곤포켓몬','Dragon Pokémon','큰 에너지를 몸에 모으고 있다.\n목과 꼬리의 수정에서 에너지를\n발산하여 주변 날씨를 바꾼다고 한다.','Dragonair stores an enormous amount of energy inside its\nbody. It is said to alter weather conditions in its vicinity by\ndischarging energy from the crystals on its neck and tail.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/148.png'),(149,'brown',0,35,45,'망나뇽','Dragonite','드래곤포켓몬','Dragon Pokémon','16시간 만에 지구를 한 바퀴 돌 수 있다.\n폭풍으로 난파 직전인 배를 발견하면\n육지까지 유도하는 상냥한 포켓몬이다.','Dragonite is capable of circling the globe in just 16 hours.\nIt is a kindhearted Pokémon that leads lost and foundering\nships in a storm to the safety of land.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/149.png'),(150,'purple',1,0,3,'뮤츠','Mewtwo','유전포켓몬','Genetic Pokémon','유전자조작을 통해 만들어진 포켓몬이다.\n인간은 과학의 힘으로 몸은 만들었지만\n상냥한 마음을 만들 수는 없었다.','Mewtwo is a Pokémon that was created by genetic\nmanipulation. However, even though the scientific power of\nhumans created this Pokémon’s body, they failed to endow\nMewtwo with a compassionate heart.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/150.png'),(151,'pink',0,100,45,'뮤','Mew','신종포켓몬','New Species Pokémon','모든 포켓몬의 유전자를 가졌다고 한다.\n자유자재로 모습을 숨길 수 있어서\n사람에게 가까이 다가가도 절대 들키지 않는다.','Mew is said to possess the genetic composition of all\nPokémon. It is capable of making itself invisible at will,\nso it entirely avoids notice even if it approaches people.','https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/151.png');
